::Epyon::

He looks at Eyebright who is sleeping in the crib. Everything was ok so
Epyon went to the main computer ban. He was able to set it to
television. Maybe he would be able to pick up some TV signals through
the transwarp rift. He got lucky and turned it to the classic sports and
entertainment channel. He sat down and proceded to watch an old RAW is
WAR show from the World Wrestling Federation.
